# Dashboard + plugin

## Dashboard

Next.js 14 · React Flow · Zustand · WebSocket · served with orchestrator in single-process mode.

Panels: flight recorder, telemetry, pending approvals (batch checkboxes), recovery.

## Obsidian plugin v0.2

- Build: `cd apps/obsidian-plugin && npm run deploy` → `vault/.obsidian/plugins/blackbox/`
- Commands: Summarize/Triage active note, Run skill picker, Review pending, Approve/Reject all pending
- **Live status:** WebSocket `/ws/global` → status bar `BB ⚙ <skill>…` (lifecycle events only; additive to 30s health/pending poll; reconnects on drop/settings change)
- Settings: orchestrator URL, API key · `main.js` gitignored in source tree

## Verify UI changes

```powershell
cd apps\dashboard && npm run build
cd apps\obsidian-plugin && npm run typecheck && npm run deploy
```
